		  <sect3>
                    <title>Zope</title>

                    <para>Zope products should install to the Zope
                      <varname>$SOFTWARE_HOME</varname> rather than
                      <varname>$INSTANCE_HOME</varname> so that they do
                      not conflict with any user-installed products that
                      might be in
                      <varname>$INSTANCE_HOME</varname>.</para>

                    <para>Zope products should also be prefixed with
                      <filename>zope-</filename> so that they do not
                      create confusion.</para>
                  </sect3>
